						               													<description>&amp;quot;It is known that from time to time Orcs perform races with steam cars, aka &amp;quot;Goratank Racing&amp;quot;. Racers, riding pimped machines, run till death on a crazy race. The winner gets a championship title, a special &amp;quot;Trophy-Gun&amp;quot;, fame and money. This competition is also known as &amp;quot;Orcorrida&amp;quot; (SpeedOrc).&amp;quot; - Lyzarbhi Chronicles&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Orcorrida is a card game where you&amp;acute;re an Orc on a deadly race that takes place at the Fields of Gore World. Prove your courage and driving skills on a competition where anything goes. During the race, Orcs release all their wildness and skills with killing machines in an exciting competition on tracks through Orc Island.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's a 3-6 player game where laughthing and fun is guaranteed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Components: 54 cards and 1 &amp;quot;pole position&amp;quot; token&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game comes in 3 languages: Portuguese, English and Orcish&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You're an orc racer and you have to play &amp;quot;road cards&amp;quot; to create your &amp;quot;path for victory&amp;quot;. You start with 5 cards and use one of them at a time to make an action. You may have an &amp;quot;Orcrook&amp;quot; card to difficult the race: missiles, mines, bump actions or turbo to increase car speed are some of the tricks you can use against the other players.&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Road cards&amp;quot; have point values and you must play them to run for victory. The player with the biggest number of points is the Champion of this crazy race.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
